1315:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c **** }
1316:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c **** 
1317:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c **** /**
1318:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Returns the CPU clock (sysa_ck) frequency
1319:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *
1320:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   The CPU clock frequency computed by this function may be not the real
1321:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         frequency in the chip. It is calculated based on the predefined
1322:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         constant and the selected clock source:
1323:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If CPUCLK source is HSI, function returns values based on HSI_VALUE(**)
1324:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If CPUCLK source is MSI, function returns values based on MSI_VALUE(*)
1325:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If CPUCLK source is HSE, function returns values based on HSE_VALUE(***)
